1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,323
Clap your hands — move your feet,

2
00:00:03,323 --> 00:00:06,646
Jump up high — feel the beat,

3
00:00:06,646 --> 00:00:09,969
Turn around — don’t be slow,

4
00:00:09,969 --> 00:00:13,292
Come on now — here we go!

5
00:00:13,292 --> 00:00:16,615
Walk, run — stop, then go,

6
00:00:16,615 --> 00:00:19,938
Stand up straight, then bend down low,

7
00:00:19,938 --> 00:00:23,261
Look around, touch the ground,

8
00:00:23,261 --> 00:00:26,584
Make a sound — louder now!

9
00:00:26,584 --> 00:00:28,799
Say “go!” — (GO!)

10
00:00:28,799 --> 00:00:31,015
Say “stop!” — (STOP!)

11
00:00:31,015 --> 00:00:33,230
Move fast — don’t drop!

12
00:00:33,230 --> 00:00:36,553
Clap your hands — move your feet,

13
00:00:36,553 --> 00:00:39,876
Jump up high — feel the beat,

14
00:00:39,876 --> 00:00:43,199
Turn around — don’t be slow,

15
00:00:43,199 --> 00:00:46,522
Come on now — here we go!

16
00:00:46,522 --> 00:00:49,845
Open, close — push, pull,

17
00:00:49,845 --> 00:00:53,168
Take it easy, now go full,

18
00:00:53,168 --> 00:00:56,491
Sit down, stand — left, right,

19
00:00:56,491 --> 00:00:59,814
Keep it moving — feel the light!

20
00:00:59,814 --> 00:01:03,137
Faster now — don’t wait,

21
00:01:03,137 --> 00:01:06,460
Move your body — feel great,

22
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:09,783
Up and down — side to side,

23
00:01:09,783 --> 00:01:13,106
Let the rhythm be your guide

24
00:01:13,106 --> 00:01:16,429
Clap your hands — move your feet,

25
00:01:16,429 --> 00:01:19,753
Jump up high — feel the beat,

26
00:01:19,753 --> 00:01:23,077
Turn around — shout it loud,

27
00:01:23,077 --> 00:01:26,400
You’re alive — feel it now!
